I'M ASKING FOR $40,000

00:17:43,362 --> 00:17:45,398
IN RETURN FOR 20% EQUITY.

00:17:45,398 --> 00:17:48,367
SO... WHILE I WAS GETTING
MY MASTER'S DEGREE

00:17:48,367 --> 00:17:50,102
AT N. Y. U. UNIVERSITY,

00:17:50,102 --> 00:17:52,605
I TOOK AN INTRODUCTORY
ELECTRONICS COURSE

00:17:52,605 --> 00:17:55,341
WHERE WE HAD TO MAKE
A DEVICE FOR THE HOME.

00:17:55,341 --> 00:17:57,910
AND I WANTED TO REMAKE
AN ALARM CLOCK.

00:17:57,910 --> 00:17:59,912
AND SO I CANVASSED
MY FELLOW STUDENTS,

00:17:59,912 --> 00:18:03,015
ASKING THEM WHAT THEIR IDEAL WAY
TO WAKE UP WAS.

00:18:03,015 --> 00:18:04,517
NOW I CAN'T SAY

00:18:04,517 --> 00:18:06,986
WHAT THE NUMBER ONE ANSWER WAS
ON TELEVISION...

00:18:06,986 --> 00:18:09,589
(laughs)
BUT THE CLOSE SECOND

00:18:09,589 --> 00:18:12,892
WAS THE SMELL
AND TASTE OF BACON.

00:18:12,892 --> 00:18:15,394
AND SO, INSPIRED,
I WENT HOME AND I BUILT

00:18:15,394 --> 00:18:17,063
THE WORLD'S FIRST ALARM CLOCK

00:18:17,063 --> 00:18:20,199
THAT ACTUALLY WAKES YOU UP
WITH BACON.

00:18:20,199 --> 00:18:21,968
(laughs)
HERE'S HOW IT WORKS‐‐

00:18:21,968 --> 00:18:24,470
SO THE NIGHT BEFORE,
YOU OPEN UP THE CHAMBER,

00:18:24,470 --> 00:18:27,740
AND YOU PUT IN A COUPLE
OF SLICES OF PRECOOKED BACON,

00:18:27,740 --> 00:18:30,142
AND THEN YOU SET THE ALARM
FOR SAY 7:00 A. M.

00:18:30,142 --> 00:18:33,813
THE NEXT MORNING AT 6:50,
THE CLOCK SILENTLY TURNS ON,

00:18:33,813 --> 00:18:36,816
AND IT HEATS UP THE BACON
TO A CRISP

00:18:36,816 --> 00:18:38,851
SO THAT THE SMELL
IS REALLY STRONG

00:18:38,851 --> 00:18:41,153
AND CAN WAKE UP
ANY BACON LOVER.
(laughs)

00:18:41,153 --> 00:18:43,589
YOU CAN THEN ACTUALLY
JUST ROLL OVER IN BED,

00:18:43,589 --> 00:18:47,193
OPEN IT UP,
AND EAT THE BACON YOURSELF.
YOU CAN COOK THE BACON
AND THEN EAT IT.

00:18:47,193 --> 00:18:49,261
THAT'S RIGHT.
<i>SHUT UP.</i>

00:18:49,261 --> 00:18:53,065
I'M SERIOUS. I BUILT THIS,
AND I THOUGHT IT WAS A LARK,

00:18:53,065 --> 00:18:55,901
SO I POSTED IT ON MY WEB SITE,
AND WAKE N' BACON WENT VIRAL.

00:18:55,901 --> 00:18:58,170
