TO SELL THEM ONE.

00:19:01,073 --> 00:19:03,075
AND SO WITH THE MONEY
I'M ASKING FOR,

00:19:03,075 --> 00:19:05,077
I WANT TO REDESIGN THIS
FOR MASS PRODUCTION

00:19:05,077 --> 00:19:06,979
