YOU‐‐YOU‐‐IT WAS
SO UNKEVIN‐LIKE WHEN YOU SAID

00:40:12,476 --> 00:40:15,645
15% ONLY TILL
WE GET OUR MONEY BACK.
ONCE WE BRING
DAYMOND INTO OUR TENT,

00:40:15,645 --> 00:40:18,448
WE‐‐WE'RE THE ONLY OFFER LEFT,
WE CAN CHANGE OUR DEAL.

00:40:18,448 --> 00:40:20,717
SO WHAT DO YOU WANT TO DO?

00:40:20,717 --> 00:40:24,121
♪♪♪

00:40:26,490 --> 00:40:29,192
(Kevin)
OKAY, BEFORE YOU SAY ANYTHING,

00:40:29,192 --> 00:40:31,194
YOU KNOW THE CURRENTS
CONSTANTLY CHANGE

00:40:31,194 --> 00:40:33,630
IN THE ROUGH WATERS
OF THE SHARK TANK.

00:40:33,630 --> 00:40:36,032
THAT'S WHY I LOVE THIS PLACE.

00:40:36,032 --> 00:40:37,868
YOUR ENEMIES
BECOME YOUR FRIENDS,

00:40:37,868 --> 00:40:40,771
YOUR FRIENDS BECOME
YOUR ENEMIES, AND SOMETIMES

00:40:40,771 --> 00:40:43,340
THEY BITE YOU IN THE HINEY
AND SOMETIMES THEY DON'T.

00:40:43,340 --> 00:40:44,941
SO WHAT'S HAPPENED IS,

00:40:44,941 --> 00:40:48,545
DAYMOND HAS DECIDED TO JOIN
MARK AND I INTO ONE OFFER.

00:40:48,545 --> 00:40:51,314
IT'S GREAT NEWS FOR YOU BECAUSE
THERE'S GONNA BE MORE MONEY,

00:40:51,314 --> 00:40:53,316
BUT I'M GONNA LET
MY PARTNER, MARK,

00:40:53,316 --> 00:40:56,386
EXPLAIN EXACTLY
HOW GREAT IT IS FOR YOU.
OKAY, SO WHAT WE'RE
GOING TO DO

00:40:56,386 --> 00:40:59,389
IS RAISE OUR OFFER
TO $750,000,

00:40:59,389 --> 00:41:03,427
AND THEN WE'RE GONNA ASK
FOR 30% OF THE COMPANY

00:41:03,427 --> 00:41:06,563
AND A 10% PERPETUAL ROYALTY.

00:41:06,563 --> 00:41:08,799
THAT'S OUR OFFER.

00:41:10,434 --> 00:41:12,869
UM, I WOULD CONSIDER
YOUR OFFER.

00:41:12,869 --> 00:41:14,971
I WOULD‐‐THE ONLY THING
I WOULD ASK YOU TO DO

00:41:14,971 --> 00:41:18,074
IS IF YOU'D GO TO $1.2 MILLION,
FOR THE SIMPLE REASON

00:41:18,074 --> 00:41:20,710
THAT WILL GIVE ME ENOUGH
TO FILL MY FIRST ORDER.
WE DON'T HAVE TO DO THAT

00:41:20,710 --> 00:41:22,712
BECAUSE IF WE OWN A PIECE
OF THE COMPANY,

00:41:22,712 --> 00:41:25,148
WE'RE YOUR PARTNERS,
THEN WE HAVE TO FINANCE YOU.

00:41:25,148 --> 00:41:29,286
BUT WE DON'T HAVE TO PAY
FOR IT RIGHT NOW.
IF YOU NEED MORE MONEY TO FUND
NEW ORDERS AND GROW THE COMPANY,

00:41:29,286 --> 00:41:31,288
YOU THINK WE'RE GONNA LET
OUR EQUITY DISAPPEAR

00:41:31,288 --> 00:41:35,258
BECAUSE WE COULDN'T FUND
A NEW ORDER? OF COURSE NOT.

00:41:35,258 --> 00:41:39,496
SO YOU GET US WITHOUT GIVING UP
ANY MORE EQUITY WITH THIS DEAL.

00:41:39,496 --> 00:41:41,465
DON'T SELL YOURSELF SHORT.

00:41:41,465 --> 00:41:43,767
JOE, LISTEN...
JOE, YOU GOTTA SAY
YES OR NO.

00:41:43,767 --> 00:41:45,769
THIS‐‐LIFE IS LIKE BUSINESS,

00:41:45,769 --> 00:41:49,105
IT'S 20% WHAT HAPPENS TO YOU
AND 80% HOW YOU RESPOND.

00:41:49,105 --> 00:41:51,107
YOU HAVE A MOMENT RIGHT NOW

00:41:51,107 --> 00:41:53,310
TO TAKE THIS DEAL.

00:41:53,310 --> 00:41:56,413
WILL YOU TAKE IT?

00:41:58,014 --> 00:42:00,951
DOES IT COME
WITH SEASON TICKETS?
ABSOLUTELY.

00:42:00,951 --> 00:42:03,086
THEN YOU GOT A DEAL.
(Daymond) AMEN.

00:42:03,086 --> 00:42:04,955
(laughing)

00:42:04,955 --> 00:42:06,323
CONGRATULATIONS.

00:42:06,323 --> 00:42:08,558
THANK YOU.
CONGRATULATIONS.

00:42:08,558 --> 00:42:11,194
CONGRATULATIONS.
REALLY GREAT JOB.
APPRECIATE IT. I'M LOOKING
FORWARD TO WORKING TOGETHER.

00:42:11,194 --> 00:42:13,230
(Mark) ABSOLUTELY.
(Robert) GOOD JOB, JOE.

00:42:13,230 --> 00:42:16,433
THANK YOU.
PLEASURE MEETING YOU.
(Barbara) DID YOU GIVE HIM
THE SEASON TICKETS?

00:42:16,433 --> 00:42:18,768
THINK ABOUT THAT. THAT'S
REMARKABLE. I JUST OFFERED A GUY

00:42:18,768 --> 00:42:21,771
$4 MILLION, WHICH IS ABOUT
AS HIGH AS I WAS GONNA GO‐‐
BUT THAT'S THE BEAUTY
OF THIS SHOW.

00:42:21,771 --> 00:42:23,807
THIS GUY WE'VE NEVER SEEN BEFORE
WALKED IN

00:42:23,807 --> 00:42:26,343
AND HAD THE CHOICE
TO BE A MILLIONAIRE...
AND HE STUCK WITH IT.

00:42:26,343 --> 00:42:28,645
AND HE STUCK TO HIS GUNS
AND HE BELIEVED IN HIMSELF.

00:42:28,645 --> 00:42:32,249
THAT'S WHAT MAKES
THIS COUNTRY GREAT.
I FEEL WARM AND FUZZY.
I JUST MADE SOME MONEY.

00:42:32,249 --> 00:42:34,784
I WOULD HAVE TO SAY,
TO TURN DOWN $4 MILLION

00:42:34,784 --> 00:42:37,787
WAS PROBABLY SOMETHING
I NEVER THOUGHT I'D SAY I DID.

00:42:37,787 --> 00:42:39,789
IT WAS SOMETHING
I NEVER THOUGHT I'D DO.

00:42:39,789 --> 00:42:42,792
BUT AT THE SAME TIME,
AT THE END OF THE DAY,

00:42:42,792 --> 00:42:45,295
I STILL GOT THREE‐QUARTERS
OF A MILLION DOLLARS,

00:42:45,295 --> 00:42:46,963
AND I STILL OWN 70%

00:42:46,963 --> 00:42:50,600
OF THE NEXT BIGGEST THING
THAT THIS WORLD'S EVER SEEN.

